<props="china">
- For fabric, trademark, generic, furniture, and industrial hardware image search, the system sets the category to 88888888 regardless of whether you specify a category.

- For generic image search, the system sets the category to 88888888 regardless of whether you specify a category.', example='88888888'),
  crop?: boolean(name='Crop', description='Specifies whether to perform subject identification. Default value: true.
