- The Region parameter has no unit. The values are based on the pixel dimensions of the image. If the image is scaled, the Region parameter values must be scaled proportionally.', example='280,486,232,351'),
  strAttr?: string(name='StrAttr', description='The string attribute. The attribute can be up to 128 characters in length. This attribute can be used to filter query results and is returned in query results.
